```plantuml
@startuml Simon-0711_ta_lyrics_sentiment_classification

actor User
participant "React Frontend" as Frontend
participant "FastAPI Backend" as Backend
participant "LyricsGenius API" as GeniusAPI
participant "Elasticsearch" as ES
participant "CNN Model" as CNN

User -> Frontend: Input song and artist
Frontend -> Backend: Send song and artist info

alt Lyrics not in Elasticsearch
    Backend -> GeniusAPI: Request lyrics
    GeniusAPI -> Backend: Return lyrics
    Backend -> ES: Store lyrics
else Lyrics in Elasticsearch
    Backend -> ES: Retrieve lyrics
end

Backend -> Backend: Preprocess lyrics
Backend -> CNN: Classify sentiment
CNN -> Backend: Return sentiment

Backend -> ES: Query similar songs
Backend -> ES: Calculate cosine similarity
ES -> Backend: Return similar songs

Backend -> Frontend: Send sentiment and recommendations
Frontend -> User: Display sentiment and recommendations

@enduml
```